title: Stereo Black (YoutubeRip) - [AlphaGuardian].zip
description:
Stereo Black (formerly New Black) was formed by Logan Mader, guitarist for Machine Head.

Stereo Black is best known for their song "Save Me" (later renamed to "Inside") featured on the trailer for the movies Max Payne, The Butterfly Effect 2 and Never Back Down 2 and their song "Denial" featured on the Scream 4 soundtrack. They were never signed and never formally released an album
